{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, physical RC and RC in general, provide a powerful method for faster and simpler multi-task learning, compared to other RNNs.",
    "Thanks to the dynamical and versatile nature of the reservoir, the RC paradigm is perfectly suited for a wide range of supervised tasks involving the processing of temporal and sequential data.",
    "These include: time series prediction, dynamical pattern generation, classification and segmentation, control, signal processing, and monitoring of rare events, among others 60.",
    "Because of all these reasons, physical RC systems have become ideal candidates for the development of novel brain-inspired computing architectures 61.",
    "In a nutshell, conn2res is an open-source Python toolbox that allows users to implement biological neural networks as reservoirs to perform cognitive tasks (https://github.com/netneurolab/conn2res)."
  ]
}